I have no problem at all finding exp groups.  Or RvR groups. <br>
<br>
And the Skald is by far the most effective at killing casters compared to any other hybrid or tank.  I think we fit in well as a dmg class but Mythic needs to be careful to not buff some class too far leaving the Skald behind.  But look at it like this you are still better off than the shammy or healer class in rvr healing and buffing in rvr is not as fun as you think =P <br>
<br>
I think Mythic just does not want the Skald class to become over popular.  It is a very attractive class.. Melee, speed, dd's, mez, snare, dmg add.  So I think we will always be one step behind the pure melee and other hybrids.  Pure melee need something to pride themselves on. =/<br>
